{
  "stem": "5644.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Didn't work long because we didn't-- we haven't been helped by an organization.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We didn't ask any to be helped.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But we did want to form ourselves.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And instead of guns, we did have pieces of sticks which we knocked at the windows and telling the peasants that we are the a group of million people.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we want some food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was the first thing [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We been given the first two, three days.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then they chased us out of the village.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They said if we come again-- most probably, they seen that this is a stick, not a gun.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We decide to stop it and to go back home, not to play partisan without an organization.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For the?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "For the?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was about-- no, I can't remember.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I been friendly right practically to the war with those two places.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I did have there friends.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "No, I can't remember names.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And after the war, I tried to go there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I been there to both places when I been and start to look for something very wrong.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I used to say to the people when I've been looking for it-- first of all, my pronunciation wasn't exactly as it should be.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because when you say, for example, Bartosze, a peasant will say Bar-to-sher.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It is changing the-- because that's a peasant.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Normally, that's Bartosze and [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, I went there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I made one big mistake when I went after the war to have a look at it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "During the war, everything was all right.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I knew where I'm going.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But after the war, 19-- that was much later.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because I went out of Poland in 1946, I think-- '45, end '45.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
